001package com.github.sormuras.bach.command;
002
003import com.github.sormuras.bach.Command;
004
005/**
006 * The jdeps command shows the package-level or class-level dependencies of Java class files.
007 *
008 * @see <a href="https://docs.oracle.com/en/java/javase/16/docs/specs/man/jdeps.html">jdeps</a>
009 */
010public record JDepsCommand(AdditionalArgumentsOption additionals) implements Command<JDepsCommand> {
011  public JDepsCommand() {
012    this(AdditionalArgumentsOption.empty());
013  }
014
015  @Override
016  public String name() {
017    return "jdeps";
018  }
019
020  @Override
021  public JDepsCommand additionals(AdditionalArgumentsOption additionals) {
022    return new JDepsCommand(additionals);
023  }
024}
